## 2. Real SSO (SAML + OIDC)

**Why:** SSO schema columns exist but nothing actually authenticates via Okta, Azure AD, Google Workspace.
Enterprise buyers require this on day 1.

Build:
- SAML 2.0 IdP-initiated + SP-initiated flow
- OIDC / OAuth 2.0 flow (Google, Microsoft, GitHub Enterprise)
- netlify/functions/sso-saml.js — parse SAML assertions, issue JWT
- netlify/functions/sso-oidc.js — OIDC callback, token exchange, issue JWT
- IDE settings panel: SSO config UI (domain, metadata URL, client ID/secret)
- JIT provisioning: auto-create user on first SSO login
- SSO-enforced orgs: block password login when SSO is on

Tools: node-saml, openid-client (or implement raw since we're serverless)

