## 3. SendGrid (Email) — Wire It Up

**What SendGrid is:** Twilio's transactional email API. You call their REST API and they
deliver emails reliably, handle spam rules, track bounces. Free up to 100/day.

**Why it's broken now:** SENDGRID_API_KEY is not set in Netlify env vars.
Password reset, email verification, invite emails, and org notifications all silently fail.

Build:
- Set SENDGRID_API_KEY in Netlify dashboard → Site settings → Environment variables
- Set SMTP_FROM_EMAIL (e.g. hello@kaixu.app)
- Set APP_URL (e.g. https://kaixu.netlify.app)
- Test: POST /auth-reset-request → should receive email
- Test: POST /auth-signup → should receive verification email
- Test: POST /invite-create → invitee should receive invite email
- Add email templates (HTML) to _lib/notify.js for nicer formatting

