## 4. Rate Limits on All Endpoints

**Why:** Right now only auth endpoints are rate-limited. Every other API is wide open to abuse.

Build:
- Apply _lib/ratelimit.js to: ai-edit, embeddings, ws-save, org-create, invite-create, comments, tasks
- Per-endpoint limits (AI is stricter, read ops are generous):
  - ai-edit: 20 req/min per user
  - ws-save: 60 req/min per user
  - embeddings: 10 req/min per org
  - org-create: 5 req/hour per user
  - invite-create: 20 req/hour per org
- Add 429 responses with Retry-After header
- Log rate limit hits to audit log

