## 5. Real Observability Stack

**Why:** DB-only error storage means you only find out something broke when a user complains.

Build:
- Sentry integration: add @sentry/node to all Netlify functions, catch + report unhandled errors
- Set SENTRY_DSN env var in Netlify
- Add Sentry to frontend (ide.html) for JS errors + source maps
- Uptime monitoring: add Netlify site to Better Uptime or UptimeRobot (free)
- Alert routing: Sentry → Slack channel on new error
- Log drains: Netlify Log Drains → Papertrail or Logtail (structured log search)

Files to modify:
- netlify/functions/_lib/logger.js — add Sentry.captureException() calls
- ide.html — add Sentry browser SDK script tag

