## 6. PDF for Client Bundle Export

**Why:** Must Haves said "zip + PDF change report" — current implementation outputs .txt not PDF.

Build:
- Use jsPDF (already have jszip.min.js, add jspdf.min.js) client-side
- exportClientBundle() in app.js: generate real PDF with:
  - Project name, date, exported by
  - File change table (filename, lines added, lines removed, last modified)
  - AI chat summary (last 10 messages)
  - Commit log (last 10 commits)
- Bundle: client-bundle-{date}.zip containing all files + CHANGE_REPORT.pdf

