## 8. Neon pgvector Extension

**Why:** RAG embeddings (embeddings.js) uses vector(1536) type — won't work until extension is enabled.
Also: embeddings.js currently calls OpenAI directly — needs to be rerouted through your Kaixu gateway.

Steps:
- Neon console → your database → SQL editor → run:
  CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS vector;
- Then run scripts/migrate.js to apply schema.sql if not already done
- Update embeddings.js: replace api.openai.com call with your Kaixu gateway endpoint
  (gateway should expose a /embeddings route that calls Gemini's text-embedding model)
- Vector dimension may need to change from 1536 (OpenAI) to match Gemini embedding output size
  (Gemini text-embedding-004 = 768 dimensions — update schema.sql: vector(768))

