## 9. Netlify Function Timeout Limits

**Why:** Default Netlify function timeout is 10s. AI operations (embeddings, ai-edit) regularly exceed this.

Build:
- netlify.toml: set [functions] timeout to 26 (max on paid plan)
- Move heavy AI ops to background functions (netlify/functions/background/) — these get 15 min
- ai-edit.js: convert to background function with polling:
  - POST /ai-edit → returns { jobId }
  - GET /ai-edit-status?jobId=... → returns { status, result }
  - Frontend polls every 2s until done
- embeddings.js: same pattern

